This case was not selected for publication in the Federal Reporter

Note: Pursuant to Fed. Cir. R. 47.6, this order is not citable as precedent.

It is a public order.

Frank BOLDUC, Plaintiff-Appellant, v. UNITED STATES, Defendant-Appellee. No. 2006-5144. United States Court of Appeals, Federal Circuit. Nov. 13, 2006.

ORDER

The order of dismissal and the mandate dated 10/31/2006 having been issued in error, the same hereby are, VACATED and RECALLED, and the notice of appeal is REINSTATED.
